  "text": "To compare the relative affinities of both mutants for the three lipid groups tested, we performed a lipid titration under the same solution conditions of 200 mM ammonium acetate buffer pH 8 supplemented with 0.5% C 8 E 5 . Titration showed a concentration-dependent binding of up to 5 lipids per AqpZ tetramer (figure 4). Binding affinities were then fitted using the sequential binding model with all free K D s using the software UniDec [CITATION_1] , supplementary figure  S2 .",
